Fitting model

fitg.Rd

Fitting model

Usage

fitg(
  data,
  boot = FALSE,
  mreg = "binomial",
  lreg = c("binomial", "gaussian", "gaussian"),
  yreg = "binomial",
  dof = 3
)

Arguments

data

input data

boot

doing bootstraping

mreg

regression model for mediator

lreg

regression model for time-varying variable

yreg

regression model for outcome variable

dof

degree of freedom

Value

fitted model
